    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know the hotlines and stuff. i've tried. it just feels like a bandaid on a bullet wound. it doesn't change the fact that life is just... a constant cycle of suffering. is it ever even okay to just give up on everything for good? like, why is it considered such a sin to just stop fighting?",
